      pearl: "The ONLY ICS-LABA combination suitable for SMART — because formoterol has rapid onset like albuterol; salmeterol-fluticasone (Advair) CANNOT be used for SMART because salmeterol has slow onset (15-30 min); GINA-preferred strategy for Steps 3-5; reduces exacerbations by 30-50% vs. fixed-dose ICS-LABA + SABA"
